\id 2JN NT0004.2J Suena NT Wilson dp transfer 5-JUN-87
\h 2 Yohane
\toc1 PAS NAMBA TU YOHANE MENI GAENUA
\toc2 2 Yohane
\mt1 PAS NAMBA TU YOHANE MENI GAENUA
\ip \it Yohane meni pas ei awa Tuara dubu zore gaenua. Nukare dumi ina-pa inoise nuarise senua. Ota dubu ami opi sai ema awa uma warise senua. \it*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 O Anutura gegenai dubu, na giti kopi zo meni nimorekare pas ei awa gainona. Na nimorekare dubara dumi me pupinowena. Awa nane gege kota, ge me susure niniro poti dube niro nowera nukare dai inowera.
\v 2 Nera kota, ge me duba nasokaira itewia itia itamunoya.
\v 3 Nakai ge mere dubara dumire puro nuanakai Anutu Mamato Yesu Kristo Mamera Mai nusoto nana ena dumi yagabare awa-diaire duba-ozaire awa semu nasokai nana niro itaise.
\s1 Dubara dumi ina-pa waira ge.
\p 
\v 4 Mama meni potai ge nuso namorekai potinua awa dubu nisokarera nana eni meni dipinoise ge me susure puro nowera ago tapisena. Susu nusokare ago ine tamuro duba naso meni yawa sara bamubake wisia.
\v 5 Are na ge zo sana niniu. Potai ge seka zo kota, matu susura ena niniro tupewenakai da awa sane. Dubara dumi ina-pa inoise nuanekai.
\v 6 Anutura potai ge dipinoise nuai ami dubara dumi me inoya. Anutura potai ge susura ena niniro tupise nowewa amira susu ego ewa: Nakai dubara dumi ina-pa inoise nuanekai.
\p 
\v 7 Ge ei awa gainona, awa nera kota, etetenai ema dainiro kei awero nowera. Nukare Yesu Kristo zebura aisore dai kei awenua amira ge awa puro ninai azu towera. Ema ago ine awa etetenai ema. Nukare ami Kristo iwo inoise nowera.
\v 8 Bua wenakare nisokare nana me wenua, awa nisokare nana ena tepo wai azu, nikare nitopekare dia inoise noiwo. Ago inoise noma me nuso bamubake pumawe.
\v 9 Ge Kristo meni tugata inoisonua ge awa zo meni kaka ziro tata-tata wamu doro ge zora bayamunoya, nu ami Anuture oko tayamunoya. Zo nu tugata wai ge puro nuamunoya ami Mamato Maire tairo nuamunoya.
\v 10 Ota zo nu tugata-magata wai ge awa kaka puro nuamu inowia ami nisokare nana mamu sai so soero oko arenawe. Dowo.
\v 11 Zo nu ema ago ine awa arenamunoya ami bua nuso waya awa soremamunoya.
\s1 Tepo wai ge.
\p 
\v 12 Ge dainiro itia ata na pas emira gayanise kaka wamu inoya. Na nisokare nana muro be meni sero niniro awamukai tona awa. Ago inoise yawa sara bamubake wanekai.
\v 13 Tuara gegenai dubu namore dai itera ami nikare arenitinora ewa. 
